sourcesContent:
import React from 'react' export const UPCPPNETOnlineForm2022 = () => { return (
Name of Post:

Uttar Pradesh UP CPPNET Admissions Online Form 2022

Post Date / Update: 07 July 2022 | 01:12 PM
Short Information : Uttar Pradesh University Medical Science (UPUMS) has released the notification of Combined Paramedical Pharmacy and Nursing Admission UPCPPNET 2022. Whoever wants to do Paramedical Courses of Uttar Pradesh, they can apply online from 07 to 16 July 2022. For admission eligibility, age limit, syllabus, course list, college list and all other information read the notification.

Uttar Pradesh University Medical Science (UPUMS)

UP Combined Paramedical Pharmacy and Nursing Admission UPCPPNET 2022 Online Form

UP CPPNET 2022 Short Details of Notification

WWW.SARKARIRESULT.COM

Important Dates

  • Application Begin : 07/07/2022
  • Last Date for Registration : 16/07/2022
  • Pay Exam Fee Last Date : 16/07/2022
  • Exam Date : 28/07/2022
  • Result Declared : Notified Soon

Application Fee (Tentative)

  • General / OBC / EWS : 2000/-
  • SC / ST : 1200/-
  • Pay the Exam Fee Through Debit Card / Credit Card / Net Banking Only.
